[The final paragraph of the first report is an edited version of the
original which contained a number of incorrect statements. It is
apparent that the local health-care authorities are still unfamiliar
with the true nature of Marburg hemorrhagic fever. For a more
accurate description of Marburg hemorrhagic fever, readers should
refer to previous posts in this thread. - Mod.CP]
